{
  "texts": [
    "This approach parses the standardised version of a dialectal sentence, and then links it to the original sentence.",
    "The standardisation is achieved using transduction, akin to n-gram decoding.",
    "However, Blodgett et al. [2018] use neural networks and present an approach to dependency parsing for African-American English.",
    "This approach uses two neural parsers, which are modified with the word embeddings used for initialisation.",
    "The word embeddings are trained on the standard and the dialect-specific datasets."
  ]
}